        "cultivation": "In temperate climate grow under cover in containers at least 30cm (12in) in diameter using soil based compost such as John Innes No.3 with added sharp sand. Maintain temperatures of 20-28\u00b0C (68-82\u00b0F) and high humidity. Apply balanced liquid feed every 2-3 weeks",
